Fabrication ,supplying, Transportation Erection & Commissioning of second stage embedded parts of  sluice gates size 3.10 mtr × 2.60 mtr (Size Tentative) Consisting of embedded parts components such as seal  beam,wheel tracks,detachable at top seal tracks. Guide rails, groovelining up to top, seal seat, seal seat bases anchorage etc. With all accessories for vertical lift fixed wheel gate including cost of materials labour, labour cess, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying one coat of zinc rich epoxy primer & three coats of cold applied coal tar epoxy paint including cutting of required R.C.C /P.C.C for fixing of embedded parts with  civil work concreting and (also designed as per latest B.I.S code with amendment if any) all complete work as per in accordance with specifications & approved drawing & direction of E/I.

Fabrication ,supply, Transportation Erection, testing & commissioning of fixed wheel type vertical lift gate(with side and bottom seal) gate leaf consisting of skin plate, structural steel horizontal & vertical girder, bottom girder, top girder, end girder vertical stiffners, wheel,wheel pin,bearing, bearing retainers rubber seal, guide shoes, lifting brackets (for loading capacity of 10 ton to 15 ton , tentative thrust capacity ) etc. With all accessories for sluice gate  all  cost of materials labour, labour cess, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying two of zinc chromate red oxide epoxy primer and three coats of approved coal tar epoxy paint including  required  civil work. (also designed  of gate leaf as per latest B.I.S code with amendment if any) all complete work as per in accordance with specifications & approved drawing & direction of E/I.

Fabrication ,supply, Transportation Erection, testing & commissioning of adequate capacity of screw hoist for U/S gates consisting of hoist screw, hoist nut, worm and worm wheel, handle,connecting nut volts, lubricating oil etc of sluice gate  (shall be designed as par latest B.I.S code with amendments if any) including cost of all materials labour, labour cess, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying two coats of zin chromate red oxide primer and three coats synthetic enamel/ alluminium paint etc. as per specification & approved drawing and direction of E/I.

Fabrication ,supplying , Transportation Erection, testing & commissioning of structural steel hoist bridge with ladder consisting of columns beams,bracing, stiffners ties, chequered plate, covering hand railing ladder with suitable rise and thread ete. With all other accessories for supporting hoisting arregement  system for operating sluice gates   including the cost of all materials  labour, labour cess, machinery, cutting aligning, anchoring, welding , finishing cleaning applying two coats  of zinc chromate red oxide primer and three coats synthetic enamel/ alluminium paint etc. as per specification & approved drawing and direction of E/I. (3 Bridge for 10 AFS Gate)
